#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Estratexias e suxestións"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
#| "cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards "
#| "that are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of "
#| "those cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the "
#| "same suit, he can play with any other card including a 'trump' card."
msgid ""
"When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
"cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards that "
"are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of those "
"cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the same suit, "
"he can play with any other card including a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""
"Cando o xogo comeza, o xogador inicial debería xogar unha das cartas con "
"face para riba do seu propio monte. Se o segundo xogador tiver cartas "
"visíbeis que sexan do mesmo pau que a carta xogada, terá de responder cunha "
"desas cartas. Se, porén, o segundo xogador non tiver unha carta do mesmo "
"pau, poderá xogar con calquera outra carta, incluíndo unha carta de «trunfo»."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is at least one 'trump' card, the highest 'trump' wins both "
#| "cards."
msgid ""
"If there is at least one <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest "
"<quote>trump</quote> wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Se existir polo menos unha carta de «trunfo», a carta de «trunfo» máis alta "
"gaña ambas as cartas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is no 'trump' card, the highest card of the suit played by the "
#| "starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If there is no <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest card of the suit "
"played by the starting player wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Se non existir unha carta de «trunfo», a carta máis alta do pau xogado polo "
"xogador inicial gaña ambas as cartas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no 'trump' "
#| "card, he has to play any card and the starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no "
"<quote>trump</quote> card, he has to play any card and the starting player "
"wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Se o xogador que responde non tiver ningunha carta do pau definido nin "
"ningunha carta de «trunfo», terá de xogar calquera carta e o xogador inicial "
"gaña ambas as cartas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The player who wins the round leads the next one."
msgstr "O xogador que gañar a rolda inicia a seguinte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Preguntas máis frecuentes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I play with a different deck of cards?"
msgstr "Podo xogar con outra baralla de cartas?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Refer to <link linkend=\"deck_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Si. Consulta <link linkend=\"deck_change\">esta</link> sección sobre a "
"«vista xeral da interface» para máis detalles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Cometín un erro. Podo desfacelo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"Non. Este xogo non ten unha funcionalidade para <quote>Desfacer</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Pódese xogar usando o teclado?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Non. Non se pode xogar a este xogo cun teclado."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Non podo entender o que facer aquí! Existe algunha suxestión?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"Non. Este xogo non ten unha funcionalidade de <quote>Suxestión</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Teño que saír do xogo, pero aínda non rematei a partida actual. Podo gardar "
"o progreso?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Save State</quote> feature."
msgstr ""
"Non, este xogo non ten unha funcionalidade para <quote>Gardar o estado</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change players' names?"
msgstr "Podo cambiar os nomes dos xogadores?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the names displayed on the right hand side of the game screen "
"refer to <link linkend=\"name_change\">this</link> section of 'Interface "
"Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Si. Para cambiar os nomes que aparecen do lado dereito da pantalla de xogo, "
"consulta <link linkend=\"name_change\">esta</link> sección sobre a «vista "
"xeral da interface» para máis detalles."

